## RULE: Dashboard = Operations, CRM = Customer Relations (Premium only)

### Dashboard Features (ALL industries get these):
- AI Calendar/Smart Scheduling
- Booking/Resource Manager
- AI Auto-Schedule
- Double Booking Guard (industry terms)
- Alerts Panel
- Industry KPIs
- Settings

### Dashboard Features (PRICING industries only — 5):
Hospitality, Airlines, Car Rental, Events, Railways
- AI Smart Pricing (edge function)
- Auto Price Alerts (>15% change notifications)
- Price Override (manual control)

